message.body: Phuong, I don't know if I'll be going tonight. My aunt died today. I haven't decided what I should do.
Oh no, I'm so sorry! It's okay, I'm still not sure myself. Are you okay?
Yeah. I'm fine. I want to go. I just don't know yet
I'm not going. My other aunt is having something at her house tonight
Okay. Sorry for your loss! Hope you feel better.
Hey, I'm sorry if this is pretty random but by any chance would you know any Hispanic females between the ages of18-24 who would be interested in shooting a commercial?
Not really. They're older than that
Well what about Mexican-born mixed Mexican/Chinese
Do you mean speak Spanish or does Eden qualify?
